Dammit Trainer
Copyright (C) 2026 Alexander Doner

Dammit Trainer is web-based software for dry-fire training in shooting
sports such as USPSA, ICORE, and bowling pin competitions. It provides
configurable target presentations and par timers for use on a screen,
television, or projected surface.

